Smith; syn.: 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Megachile atratula" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atratula">Megachile atratula</taxonomicName>
Rebmann (see 
<bibRefCitation author="Gonzalez, VH" journalOrPublisher="Journal of the Kansas Entomological Society" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" pagination="58 - 67" title="A new species of Megachile from Pakistan, with taxonomic notes on the subgenus Eutricharaea (Hymenoptera: Megachilidae)." url="https://doi.org/10.2317/JKES0905.16.1" volume="83" year="2010">Gonzalez et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
